OL,5, The publisher of the Mirror newspapers 
OL,6, has made a court apology to the former 
OL,7, Coronation Street actor Nikki Sanderson
OL,8, after admitting using private          
OL,9, investigators to get stories about her.
OL,11,FA barrister for Mirror Group Newspapers
OL,12,Fsaid it "unequivocally apologises" to  
OL,13,Fher, adding "it shouldn't have happened
OL,14,Fand won't again".                      
OL,16,FMs Sanderson was giving evidence in her
OL,17,FHigh Court case against the newspapers.
OL,19,FDespite the admissions, MGN denies     
OL,20,Ftargeting her more widely.             
